https://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/utilities/xcu_chap02.html


lsapp = first word
Make = second word

> |lsapp
> ls ls|>&Make +
> ls ls|lsapp
> |&lsapp
> |>&Make -
> |>& Make


>      lsapp>&
> | >&Make

> lsapp |lsapp>&Make |>&Make >&&lsapp >&&&Make
> as &lsapp &&lsapp &&&lsapp
>





